<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>비만도 측정 | Kcal-cal</title>
  <!-- favicon -->
  <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/static/img/favicon.png" type="image/x-icon">
  <!-- css: reset -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/css/reset.css">
  <!-- css: header -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/css/header.css">
  <!-- css : sub -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/css/sub.css">
  <!-- fontawsome -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.8.2/css/all.min.css">
  <!-- xelcon -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="//cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/xeicon@2.3.3/xeicon.min.css">
  <!-- jQuery CDN -->
  <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/2.2.4/jquery.min.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
  <div id="wrap">
    <%- include('header.ejs') %>

    <!-- main content -->
    <main id="sub1">
      <section>
        <h2 class="hidden">Main Content</h2>
        <article class="BMI">
          <h3>키와 몸무게로 간단하게 자신의 비만도(BMI)를 확인해 보세요.</h3>

          <div class="form">
            <form id="bmiCheckForm" name="bmiCheckForm">
              <h4>신체정보</h4>
              
              <label for="length">신장</label>
              <input type="text" id="length" name="length"><span>cm</span>
              <br>

              <label for="weight">체중</label>
              <input type="text" id="weight" name="weight"><span>kg</span>
              <br>

              <span class="compute">
                <input type="button" id="btnCalc" value="계산">
                <input type="reset" value="초기화">
              </span>
            </form>

            <!-- 비만도 결과값 -->
            <ul id="result">
              <li>
                <h4 class="text"></h4>
                <p id="resultText"></p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <h4 class="number"></h4>
                <p id="bmiNumber"></p>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="info">
            <h4>비만도(BMI)란?</h4>
            <p>
              체질량지수는 카우프지수로 비만을 평가하는 지수이며
              세계적으로 쓰이는 공통표준 지수입니다.
              체지방의 정도를 표준체중보다 비교적 정확하게 반영할 수 있고
              매우 간단히 규정할 수 있는 장점이 있습니다.
            </p>

            <h4>비만도의 산출방법</h4>
            <p>체질량지수 = 체중 &#40; kg &#41; / 키의 제곱 &#40; &#13217; &#41;</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="BMIgraph">
          <h3 class="hidden">BMI 그래프로 확인하기</h3>
          <!-- <ul class="graph">
            <li>저체중</li>
            <li></li>
            <li></li>
            <li></li>
          </ul> -->

          <p class="graphResult">결과가 궁금하시다면 신장과 체중을 입력해주세요!</p>

          <ul class="graph">
            <li>
              <label>BMI</label>
              <label class="dv1">18.5</label>
              <label class="dv2">23</label>
              <label>25.00</label>
              <ul class="clearfix">
                <li class="low-weight">저체중</li>
                <li class="regular">정상</li>
                <li class="overweight">과체중</li>
                <li class="obesity">비만</li>
              </ul>
              <label>체중</label>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </article>
      </section>
    </main>
  </div>
  <!-- 비만도 측정 js -->
  <script src="/static/js/sub1.js"></script>
</body>

</html>